import React from 'react'
import Banner from './Banner'
import Categories from './Categories'
import Posts from './Posts'
import {Box,Button, Grid} from '@material-ui/core'


function Home() {
    return (
        <>
        <Banner />
        <Grid container styles={{marginTop:"10px"}}>
            <Grid item>
                <Categories />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
                <Posts />
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
        </>
    )
}

export default Home
